social_posts.post_text: @pairofthieves it was an honor to be a part of your project 🩲🩳

PASSAIC NJ HAS PRIDE BECAUSE OF DIANA TIBURCIO!!!! i’m so proud of you for organizing and hosting Pride for your hometown. despite a harassing mayor and homophobic party crashers YOU single-handedly brought Pride to your community. you inspire me. -your biggest fan <3 🏳️‍⚧️
🌟wishing the happiest golden birthday to my baby Emmy🌟
